  <name>preCICE Config Visualizer</name>
  <summary>Interactive visualizer for preCICE configuration files</summary>

  <developer id="org.precice">
    <name>preCICE Developers</name>
  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>The preCICE Config Visualizer visualizes preCICE configuration files as an interactive graph.</p>
    <p>This tool produces visual graph representation of the various participants, communicators and meshes defined in the setup and the movement of data between them.</p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Supports configurations of preCICE version 2 and 3</li>
      <li>Reduce or hide various parts of information</li>
      <li>Export in various formats</li>
      <li>Export unprocessed dot for additional customization</li>
      <li>Autoreload on file change</li>
      <li>Copy PNG to clipboard for easy sharing</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

